Folder and file structure:

config_array.php // file holds all the sites default setup
front_files // holds the main site files such as home, about, contact
gallery // a sample gallery system file
index.php // the core file that all the data is loaded into
main_array.php // holds the sites main navigation list
news // a sample news system
products // a sample folder with sub files
system // holds the core system elements
templates // holds all chosen templates
user_images // holds site specific images for main pages, news etc.